{"tid":873853,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)石破天驚","createTime":"2018-10-23T17:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T19:36:00.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f26b5263548d675768be3c2420ea65546b5d683","tid":873853,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=h6uZphh8S9XPyjlMgbYC8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6649137f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=h6uZphh8S9XPyjlMgbYC8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f0765ee6\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=h6uZphh8S9XPyjlMgbYC8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9d4d457b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/danlkaelb/1320245400-901803871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdanlkaelb%2F1320245400-901803871.jpg&h=d94dd39e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在1963年以前，位於舊金山外海的惡魔島以嚴密的警衛措施，成為全美犯人聞之喪膽的魔鬼監獄，固若金湯的天牢設計，讓重刑犯如同囚禁在銅牆鐵壁之中。監獄廢棄後，惡魔島成了觀光勝地，每日都有遊客湧進其中，嘗試坐牢的滋味。然而此時惡魔島卻落在一群軍人的手裡，成為他們臨時的基地<br />\n<br />\n1 45AM左右